@governance @critical
Feature: AI Commit CXO/Board Level Posture Tests
  As an executive or board member
  I want assurance that aicommit meets strategic business objectives
  So I can trust our technology investments and risk posture

  Background:
    Given aicommit is properly installed
    And a git repository is initialized
    And the working directory is clean

  Scenario: Strategic Alignment Validation
    Given organizational strategic objectives exist
    When I evaluate strategic alignment
    Then aicommit should support digital transformation goals
    And innovation objectives should be advanced
    And competitive advantage should be enhanced
    And business agility should be improved
    And Strategic alignment should be demonstrably achieved

  Scenario: Business Value Realization
    Given business value metrics are defined
